# .dockerignore
#
# Files yang TIDAK dibawa ke Docker build context.
# Critical: jangan copy data sensitif (.env), binary lokal, atau IDE files.

# --- Build artifacts ---
bin/
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# --- Data / state ---
data/
*.db
*.db-journal
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# --- Secrets ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- IDE / OS ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Git ---
.git/
.gitignore

# --- Docs (tidak dibutuhkan di runtime image) ---
docs/
*.md
!README.md

# --- Coverage ---
coverage.out
coverage.html

# NOTE: kita JANGAN exclude *_test.go karena `go build` skip mereka otomatis,
# dan kalau di-exclude, test paket internal masih bisa break referensi.
#
# JANGAN exclude `docker/` karena docker-compose embedder pakai context
# `./docker/embedder/` (kalau di-ignore, build context kosong).
#
# JANGAN exclude `Dockerfile` / `docker-compose*.yml` — Docker engine tidak
# perlu mereka di build context, tapi exclusion di sini tidak salah; tetap
# kita biarkan included agar tidak misleading.

# --- Logs ---
*.log
logs/
